{"tid":404712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】林門鄭氏委任唐英年掌西九管理局，打破政務司司長兼任慣例","createTime":"2017-09-18T10:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T11:33:06.000Z","uid":35221,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71166f330ef4f97e9e943d24b85c9df9162ebee7","tid":404712,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:13:24.000Z","msg":"港聞<br />\n2017年9月18日 星期一 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭委任唐英年掌西九管理局　打破政務司長兼任慣例 (17:01)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170918/s00001/c98cc8b7bfa4c7eb1e07a31034a50bdf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170918%2Fs00001%2Fc98cc8b7bfa4c7eb1e07a31034a50bdf.jpg&h=7b2bebf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1 - （資料圖片／明報製圖）<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥宣布，任命前政務司長唐英年擔任西九管理局新主席，今年10月1日接任，任期兩年，打破過往由現任政務司長擔任這職位的慣例。唐英年曾經是西九管理局首任主席，今次是再度獲委任。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥讚揚唐英年有豐富公共行政經驗，是出色企業家，形容他是帶領西九邁向新發展階段的最理想人選。<br />\n<br />\n西九管理局主要負責發展、協調及統籌西九文化區事務，過往管理局主席皆由時任政務司長兼任，包括唐英年、林瑞麟、林鄭月娥，以及現任政務司長張建宗。<br />\n<br />\n轉自明報新聞網<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170918/s00001/1505722991204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170918%2Fs00001%2F1505722991204&d=wNMYcH0LSDsdc%2F3Ij%2BkB6viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=eb1a94ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170918%2Fs00001%2F1505722991204&h=346646d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170918/s00001/1505722991204</a>"},{"pid":"7adffca242ebe22373d7785d91aab0dccb6d248d","tid":404712,"uid":71205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f59c0a0d56260e7eaf2f6729e96e7f3dbe9129b","tid":404712,"uid":36178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:23:27.000Z","msg":"三剎位"},{"pid":"e62e94f6a9c1a94841ed875f818f49219166f150","tid":404712,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:24:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三剎位</blockquote><br />\n為皇兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b45063e82f64c11bd452e5a0c4abf43cf7cb27e","tid":404712,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:31:12.000Z","msg":"見到張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15db6be560e457a8c6853c97c48254f505ddd83c","tid":404712,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:53:55.000Z","msg":"兩條友都唔同level"},{"pid":"b3ee4c1f945919da21cb7afd367eeb2d7fdc1779","tid":404712,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:37:29.000Z","msg":"唐唐強項官傷勾結，成個都係地產project . 無搵錯人"},{"pid":"ed88309da19a894ce12b502009154c022c99e6cb","tid":404712,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:50:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啲政府高層做來做去嗰班人"},{"pid":"54c22909db8c8f32c91d8b37fd129878b9a207c1","tid":404712,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:54:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b89af66d816d75986c848e881b5db1c25d3a883c","tid":404712,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:33:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}